{"id": "art-66", "label": "Art. 66", "title": "Art. 66", "slug": "art-66", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 66 </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>(1)Pe\ndurata <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>, creditorii asociatului\npot s&#259;-<span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> exercite drepturile lor numai\nasupra <span class=SpellE>p&#259;r&#355;ii</span> din beneficiile cuvenite\nasociatului dup&#259; <span class=SpellE>bilan&#355;ul</span> contabil, iar\ndup&#259; dizolvarea <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>, asupra <span\nclass=SpellE>p&#259;r&#355;ii</span> ce i s-ar cuveni prin lichidare.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_848274437\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2431\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_848274437\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Creditorii <span class=SpellE>prev&#259;zu&#355;i</span>\nla alin. (1) pot <span class=SpellE>totu&#351;i</span> popri, în timpul duratei\n<span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>, <span class=SpellE>p&#259;r&#355;ile</span>\nce s-ar cuveni <span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;ilor</span> prin lichidare sau\npot sechestra <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> vinde <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iunile</span>\nori <span class=SpellE>p&#259;r&#355;ile</span> sociale ale debitorului lor.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_882529958\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2430\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_882529958\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)Ipoteca legal constituit&#259; asupra <span\nclass=SpellE>ac&#355;iunilor</span> sau <span class=SpellE>p&#259;r&#355;ilor</span>\nsociale poate fi executat&#259; potrivit <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>legii</i>,\nAdministratorii/Membrii directoratului sunt <span class=SpellE>obliga&#355;i</span>\ns&#259; pun&#259; la <span class=SpellE>dispozi&#355;ia</span> creditorului\nipotecar sau a organului de executare, la cererea acestora, <span class=SpellE>situa&#355;iile</span>\nfinanciare <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> orice alte înscrisuri ori <span\nclass=SpellE>informa&#355;ii</span> necesare evalu&#259;rii <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iunilor</span>\nsau <span class=SpellE>p&#259;r&#355;ilor</span> sociale, precum <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> s&#259; faciliteze preluarea acestora.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}